        {
            "title": "22萬股東嗨翻！國票金經營權大戰將至 紀念品價值翻倍大方送「法蘭絨毯」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2JuYExl0TjzKdtzDPm1zOA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/cccb5a8356e8c118edf018fddae96c5f\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
